                  </hi>. Aged 19.—<hi rend="italic">Recommended to mercy by the Prosecutor</hi>.</p>
               <xptr type="pageFacsimile" doc="183508170016"></xptr>
               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Third Jury, before Mr. Baron Alderson.</hi>
